        <h1>Remedies for dandruff</h1>
        <h2>Coconut oil and lemon:</h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>Coconut oil is something that everyone's grandmother advices. 
            Its antifungal properties can provide a great relief from itchiness and dry scalp.</p>
        <p>How to apply this?</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Combine equal amounts of coconut oil and lemon juice and massage the mixture on your scalp. </li>
            <li>Keep it for about 10-15 minutes and rinse your hair thoroughly.</li>
            <li>Make sure to preheat the oil in winter as it tends to freeze easily in colder temperatures.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>This will not only help you get rid of dandruff but also boost hair growth and nourishment. </p>
