        <h2>Yogurt:</h2>
            <div class="xyz">
                <div class="pqr">
            <p>The lactic acid in yogurt helps reduce dandruff and the protein in it strengthens your hair from its roots. 
                It is a treasure trove of friendly bacteria and helps prevent flaking of the scalp area.</p>
            <p>How to apply this?</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Apply a layer of fresh yogurt on the scalp and hair.</li>
                <li>Let it sit for 10-15 minutes and rinse with lukewarm water and dry.</li>
                <li>You can try adding black pepper to yogurt since that is also loaded with anti fungal properties.</li>
            </ol>
                </div>
