        <h2>Neem:</h2>
            <div class="xyz">
                <div class="pqr">
            <p>Because of its antibacterial, anti fungal and antimicrobial properties, it is a simple cure for dandruff and itchiness.
                A homemade neem pack is the easiest remedy for dandruff.
            </p>
            <p>How to apply this?</p>
            <ol>
                <li>All you have to do is take some neem leaves, grind them in the mixer and add a tablespoon of honey to it.</li>
                <li> Once it becomes a thick paste, put it all over the scalp like a hair mask and allow it to stay for 20 minutes. </li>
                <li>Wash it when it is suitably dry and watch the wonders it does to your scalp.</li>
            </ol>
                </div>
